drink they have already made the decision 
montgomery county is the only local government in the nation 
that controls the wholesale distribution of alcoholic beverages it 
provides beer and wine to retailers in the county and it has a 
monopoly on the sale of hard liquor four other counties in 
maryland have a less strict form of liquor control and 18 states 
have liquor control 
we walk a fine line baylin said basically we are here 
to foster moderation temperance and respect of the law but on the 
