chicago and houston the epidemic in five southern california 
counties is the nations biggest and has sputtered and flared for 
more than two years 
its very hard to keep control in a large urban area where you 
have a large influx of people from other countries dr gary 
euler of the san bernardino county public health department said 
thursday 
