this is a radio station where arbitron numbers 
are arbitrary everybody has to listen you cant change the dial 
you cant turn it down you cant turn it off 
you can however leave the store 
its rite aid radio a station created solely for the drug store 
chain morning drive afternoon drive it doesnt matter the only 
