day 
pop is not what the stations play its an acronym for point of 
purchase a fastgrowing phenomenon in which the stores create 
their own format for an instore sound system 
they dont want shock jocks or top 40 screamers youll never 
hear gooooood morninnnnnng aampp while cruising the frozen 
food aisle or catch highway to hell cranking out while you 
